        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals33"/>
        <p><span class="strong"><strong>Carrying Capacity:</strong></span> A light load for a <a href="ch73s10.html#MonstersAnimals32">camel</a> is up to 300 pounds; a medium load, 301-600 pounds; and a heavy load, 601-900 pounds. A <a href="ch73s10.html#MonstersAnimals32">camel</a> can drag 4,500 pounds.</p>
